snippet.title: Dead by Daylight | Charity Case Console release
snippet.description:
The Charity Case is a collection of 26 cosmetics inspired by some of our most loyal Content Creators and it is coming on Console!
Release December 4th on XBOX, PS4 NA, PS4 Japan
PS4 EU is still in standby.

Join the official forum: https://forum.deadbydaylight.com/en/
Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DeadByDaylight/
